testsuite.name: au.org.ala.ecodata.LockServiceSpec

testcase.name: a lock can only be obtained once
a lock can be released once obtained
a lock can be released by a different user to the one that obtained it
an executeWithLock block can be executed by a user holding the lock
an executeWithLock block cannot be executed when another user holds the lock
an executeWithLock block can be executed when the entity is not locked
